                  <persName ref="PRS5816Kabbada"><roleName type="title">āzzāž</roleName></persName>. 
                  During the Italian occupation (1936-1941), he was in exile in <placeName ref="Q1218"/>. 
                        After liberation, he served in various important government posts until the revolution, in<date>1974</date>. 
